      • callbackContextMap

        protected java.util.Map<java.lang.Long,JavetCallbackContext> callbackContextMap
        The Callback context map.

        V8 may not make final callback when V8 context is being recycled. That may result in memory leak. Callback context map is designed for closing that memory leak issue.

        Since:
        0.8.3
